Conky Metro Clock is a minimalist conky configuration which resembles the Metro Style clock appearing in the Windows 8 screensaver. The font used is "Open Sans Light".

Nothing fancy. Just shows date and time.

---

Installation Instructions:

1. First install conky if you don't have it.

2. Extract the files .conkyrc and .conky_start.sh to your home folder.

3. Run "chmod +x ~/.conky_start.sh" in a Terminal.

3. Add ~/.conky_start.sh to your Startup Applications.

4. Enjoy!

